-- European Stocks Advance as Spanish Banks Rally; Santander, Popular Climb
-- Andrew Rummer
-- 2010-07-07T13:32:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/european-stocks-advance-as-spanish-banks-rally-santander-popular-climb.html

          
          
             European stocks advanced, erasing an
earlier decline, as Banco Santander SA and Banco Popular Espanol
SA led a rally in Spanish banks.  
 The Stoxx Europe 600 Index rose 0.2 percent to 243.21 at
2:30 p.m. in London, having previously lost as much as 1.5
percent.  
          
          


  


        